                                .tab-content
                                    #patient.tab-pane.active
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8
                                                p 
                                                | (If patient is unable to answer, PCG can answer)
                                                input(type="text" name="patient_01").ipt-sm
                                            .col-sm-4 
                                                label(for="patient_02")
                                                    input(type="checkbox" name="patient_02") 
                                                    | No Limitations
                                        hr 
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
