                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm
                                                        option(value="") Required for HIS--> 
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
                                                | CPR Preference(DNR/Code Status)?
                                            .col-md-4 
                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm
                                                        option(value="") Required for HIS--> 
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
                                                | Wants Other Life-Sustaining Treatment Preferences (Other than CPR)
                                            .col-md-4 
                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm 
                                                        option(value="") Required for HIS-->  
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8   
                                                | Does Pt/Family want to avoid hospitalization?
                                            .col-md-4 
                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm.aler-success
                                                        option(value="") Select-->
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
                                                | Any special event/ desire for patient before dying?
                                            .col-md-4 
                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm 
                                                        option(value="") Select--> 
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
                                                | Able to understand and participate in own care?
                                            .col-md-4 
                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm  
                                                        option(value="") Select--> 
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
                                                | Is there a need for an interpreter?
                                            .col-md-4 
                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm  
                                                        option(value="") Select--> 
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
                                                | If Yes, offer of interpreter
                                            .col-md-4 
                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm  
                                                        option(value="") Select--> 
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
                                                | Has Patient/Spouse served in the military?
                                            .col-md-4
                                                .form-group.has-success 
                                                    select.ipt-sm  
                                                        option(value="") Select--> 

                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
                                                | Is Patient able to safely administer meds?
                                            .col-md-4 
                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm  
                                                        option(value="") Select--> 
                                        
                                        .row 
                                            .col-md-8 
                                                | If No, who is able to safely administer meds to Patient?
                                            .col-md-4 
                                                .form-group.has-success
                                                    select.ipt-sm  
                                                        option(value="") Select--> 
                                                    input(type="text" placeholder="Others").ipt-sm
                                        
                                        
                                    #pcg.tab-pane
                                        p TAB 2
                                    #envi.tab-pane
                                        p TAB 3
                                    #mobility.tab-pane
                                        p TAB 4
                                    #adl.tab-pane
                                        p TAB 5
                                    #dme.tab-pane
                                        p TAB 6
                                    #iv.tab-pane
                                        p TAB 7
                               


